<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[السَّويُّ]</span>: السالم،<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>بَشَراً سَوِيًّا <span class="c2">«٥»</span>.<span class="c5"> وقوله تعالى:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>صِرااطاً سَوِيًّا <span class="c2">«٦»</span>: أي مستقيماً.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
